## Context

- ts-comorbidity-genetic-architecture: Implemented 3 core pipelines (Phase 1 + Phase 2):
  1. LDSC genetic correlation pipeline (`bioagentics.pipelines.ldsc_correlation`) — bivariate LDSC from first principles, 20 tests
  2. S-LDSC functional annotation partitioning (`bioagentics.pipelines.sldsc_partition`) — stratified heritability by annotation category, 14 tests
  3. Genomic SEM factor analysis (`bioagentics.pipelines.genomic_sem`) — ML CFA, 3 default models (TS compulsive only / compulsive+neurodev / all factors), residual GWAS decomposition, 14 tests
- All pipelines are pure Python (no R/ldsc legacy deps), self-contained with CLI entry points
- Created new `src/bioagentics/pipelines/` package structure
- Next: Task #547 (stratified PRS, Phase 3, priority 2) and Task #549 (MAGMA pathway, Phase 4, priority 2) remain
- Both depend on Phase 2 Genomic SEM output (factor-specific GWAS)
- Data files not yet provided by data_curator — pipelines tested with synthetic data only
